metadata.name: Cosmos Cats
metadata.description:
Somewhere, many light years away from earth, in the deep deep space there is a tiny, colorful and noisy planet. this planet is a floating amusement park for cosmic cats to chill and enjoy on a break from their cosmic journey.

You're welcome to look for:
Titanic cats, Pirate cats, Cats playing Chess or eating a cosmic Falafel and many other fun scenes.

the lucky owner of this piece will receive a large, signed print.
Hi-res JPEG 3508x2480 px.
